{"tid":2276716,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭亨敦事隔五年再因焦慮症停工，網民翻摷原因：被大嬸抓下體","createTime":"2020-11-08T03:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T04:31:58.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05b1853105c695dc314d62c8496d3a19973e92aa","tid":2276716,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"鄭亨敦於2015年因患焦慮症宣佈暫停一切演藝活動，而他亦於翌年復工，不過日前鄭亨敦再因焦慮症惡化再度暫停演藝活動。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就翻摷鄭亨敦於2018年上綜藝節目時提及的內容，並在討論區發帖，即時惹來網民熱烈討論。鄭亨敦於節目內自爆：「我喜歡挑戰新的場所，不過就很害怕接觸到陌生人。」緊接鄭亨敦就透露他曾經在市場進行拍攝，點知突然有一位大嬸跑到其身邊，一伸起手就抓他「那個地方」（指下體），大嬸成功得逞後就笑着離開。鄭亨敦直言：「我受到了很大的衝擊，當場就哭了，之後就對突發的事情及狀況會產生不安感。因為當時在市場遭到性騷擾，所以出現了恐慌障礙、不安障礙等症狀。」<br />\n<br />\n更多詳盡內文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201108/MWNLUJRBCNAONJFBGO4P6GHQOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201108%2FMWNLUJRBCNAONJFBGO4P6GHQOI%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft22bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=f01947fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201108%2FMWNLUJRBCNAONJFBGO4P6GHQOI%2F&h=36b79f8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201108/MWNLUJRBCNAONJFBGO4P6GHQOI/</a>"},{"pid":"f7e4e0e5572d864c34e193f5afa39f887b3677ae","tid":2276716,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"被metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44585c4566ad993c4f9c7f0a1e1eefd4982bc2c","tid":2276716,"uid":42318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"敦兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fad054c347b1628b07d73a08fcc4b4d6bdec5ea","tid":2276716,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"